name: Xtra Xanax
description: Gonna need an extra one after this sight...  This artwork was created as part of the #Legato100 project, as a cover art for "Nifty Sax: Genesis #50 - Xtra Xanax". Legato100 is a collaborative project of 100 artworks for 100 music tracks. The track is available here: https://bit.ly/NiftySax-50, Project's official page: https://niftysax.com/legato100
